Theer are 3 types of error I need to validate - 

One is 400 - where we need to verify description and validationErrors.error (BP not found or type not found) as shown below - 

{
    "description": "Validation Errors",
    "validationErrors": [
        {
            "value": "?",
            "error": "BP not found"
        },
        {
            "value": "bpId and personId are null",
            "error": "bpId or personId must be set"
        }
    ]
}

or this - 

{
    "description": "Validation Errors",
    "validationErrors": [
        {
            "value": "xxx",
            "error": "Type not found"
        }
    ]
}

